$$ IR=\left(\frac{Pim}{Pt}\right)\ast 1000 $$
\end{document}IR=PimPt∗1000
Out-migration rate = (Number of persons leaving an administrative area/population in the area)∗1000. That is, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
